# Key Components

BookingWidget, SlotPicker, MapListSwitcher, RatingStars, WalletCard, ChatPanel, TrackingMap, AvailabilityEditor.
AdminTable, KycReviewModal, DisputeResolutionWizard.

Tech Choices

UI: TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui; Headless components; Lucide icons.
State: React Query (TanStack) for data fetching; Zustand for local UI state.
i18n: next-intl with AR RTL.
Maps: MapLibre/Leaflet (open-source) or Google Maps if desired.
Forms: React Hook Form + Zod schema validation.